data.description: This classic cottage design of the Egret floor plan offers an immediately available home in the Cottage Park section of River Bluffs. Step in the front door and the home welcomes you to the main living area, dining area with built-in bench seating and kitchen with drybar/butler's pantry. Also on the main is a guest suite with full bath that offers your guests their own private suite or a wonderful at-home office. Upstairs the loft at the landing is a cozy lounge that centers the layout to branch off to each of the bedrooms. The primary suite offers ample storage with two walk-in closets and a bright bathroom. Two more guestrooms are located on the second floor with the larger room over the garage having its own private bath. In total this home is just over 2300 square feet with four bedrooms and four and a half baths and is located a very short walk (or golf cart ride) to the marina and one of the community's pools. The gated community of River Bluffs also offers a boat ramp, pools, fitness centers, a half mile riverwalk, community farm and much more.  River Bluffs Sales office is open Monday-Saturday 10-5 and Sunday 1-5.
